    base:desc "Design (requirements R1–R8 and architecture mapping), Simulation (ROS2-based prototyping), Implementation (component packaging, sensor integration, ROS2 nodes), Integration (data pipeline and actuation wiring), Deployment (cloud hosting and PT connectivity), Runtime Operation (real‑time monitoring, remote control, and maintenance via data analytics)."
