    base:desc "Real‑time data pipelines ensuring 100 ms end‑to‑end latency; 100 ms clock synchronization across distributed nodes; verification of ACC logic against ISO 15622 specifications; validation of DBSCAN/Kalman models against simulated ground truth; continuous integration in ROS2 leading to automated regression testing of data translation and actuation correctness."
]

