    base:desc "Logical network: Wi‑Fi (IEEE 802.11ac) between PT and DT hosts; physical links: Ethernet/USB to PT sensors; data transport: ROS2 over DDS providing QoS settings for real‑time streaming; Data Translation FE performs serialization (likely JSON or binary) and unit conversion for remote transmission."
